rows.label: bf01070100_0020

Going all right, else
I wouldn't be here.

rows.label: bf01070100_0030
rows.name: Fair point. So which one am I unloading?

rows.label: bf01070100_0040
rows.name:
We can leave that until I'm done
negotiating. Shouldn't be too long!

rows.label: bf01070100_0050
rows.name: Well, mooring is 15 gold per half-day.

rows.label: bf01070100_0060
rows.name:
I'll have your gold after I sell
the stuff, all right? Later!

rows.label: bf01070100_0080
rows.name:
You know I can't do credit... *sigh*
He does it every time, too...

rows.label: bf01070100_0120
rows.name:
This thing's huge, and it's
not even a Divine Beast ship!
